Vramsteg has been built and tested on the following configurations:

  * OS X 10.8 Mountain Lion and 10.7 Lion
  * Debian 7.0 Wheezy (stable) and 6.0 Squeeze (oldstable) plus Sid (testing)

---

While Vramsteg has undergone testing, bugs are sure to remain.  If you
encounter a bug, please send a message to:

  support@yootabory.com

and check for updates at http://tasktools.org.

Thank you.
